    • Gebruiker

      public Gebruiker(String email, String wachtwoord, String naam, boolean isActief, Rol rol)
      Constructs a new Gebruiker with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      rol - enum Rol role of this user
      email - the login email linked to this user
      wachtwoord - the login password linked to this user
      naam - the name of this user
      isActief - boolean status of this user: active/inactive
      adres - the Adres object representing this user's address
